channel.title: The story of me and Moparscape
channel.description: I once was a player of Runescape, until I found my way into Private Servers...Then, I registered here, and then made another account(I have no Idea why) and became a Senior Member on that one, then got banned for trying to get back someguy that CRASHED my server COMPLETELY to the ground...Deleted my server post, hacked my computer...EVERYTHING!So, there I was banned for 1 year...I still have the first account I made...I'm posting as it right now....
